title: 229. Andy & DJ CTI: Rumble's $100 Million Offer, Canada's Freedom Convoy Fuel & Department Of Health Ends Requirements
itunes:title: 229. Andy & DJ CTI: Rumble's $100 Million Offer, Canada's Freedom Convoy Fuel & Department Of Health Ends Requirements
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Rumble offering the Joe Rogan Experience 100 million dollars to bring over his podcast censorship free, Canadians being threatened by the Ottawa police for bringing fuel to the truckers protest, and the US Department Of Health ending the requirements for hospitals to report daily Covid-19 deaths.
